{"tid":1309732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣傳媒》「暴動」公文打臉港府 民陣痛批：謊言治港","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:51:55.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77b2385198f56c2b72dc752c31dbcc49cae830d2","tid":1309732,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"反送中》「暴動」公文打臉港府 民陣痛批：謊言治港<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-12<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕近來香港政府頻頻否認將6月12日的反送中示威行動定性為「暴動」。今日正值鎮壓滿月，「民間人權陣線」召集人岑子杰公開，6月12日晚間香港警方發出的「反對通知書」證明警方對該場集會遊行的定性確為「暴動」。「民間人權陣線」痛批，政府一再以謊言治港，真誠何在？<br />\n<br />\n「民間人權陣線」今在臉書上發文指出，「今日是612鎮壓一周月，民陣翻查警方文件，發現早前警方發給民陣的文件中，清楚指明『警方已於同日將上述地點舉行的集會定性為暴動』，而且『上述地點』更包括『中信大廈』，即是幾近人踩人的鎮壓場所，而盧偉聰、林鄭月娥更多番向公眾指，政府、警隊沒有就事件作出定性。」<br />\n<br />\n「民間人權陣線」痛批，「政府一再謊言治港，附圖信件的文字清楚指出範圍，定性，為何整場風暴已經翻天覆地至如斯地步，你們仍然自以為謊言、公關技倆可以糊弄港人？你們的誠意何在，真誠何在？」<br />\n<br />\n在今日的記者會場，岑子杰表示，目前正與法律團對研擬追究警方在和平集會上使用武力清場的問題。岑子杰要求，獨立調查委員會應儘快設立，才能還原示威真相，並儘快撤回暴動定性，「不要再抹黑示威者」。<br />\n<br />\n目前「民間人權陣線」正在申請7月21日晚間集會的不對通知書，該場集會料將以設立獨立調查委員會、徹查警方多次暴力行為等訴求重返金鐘。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2351767344870643/?type=3&amp;refsrc=http%3A%2F%2Fd-30441735681743803905.ampproject.net%2F1907022322580%2Fframe.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.680202458693815%2F2351767344870643%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26refsrc%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fd-30441735681743803905.ampproject.net%252F1907022322580%252Fframe.html&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUygKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=e3a5b1bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2351767344870643/?type=3&amp;refsrc=http%3A%2F%2Fd-30441735681743803905.ampproject.net%2F1907022322580%2Fframe.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2850988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2850988&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUygKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=ffa204fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2850988</a>"},{"pid":"7790680e46514e16ca3c3ba2d84ef4e4b6918144","tid":1309732,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a433f15b024160bade1593a3741cf74782e91d","tid":1309732,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309d01899160fd3c4fe91cc30513cb70326a0c60","tid":1309732,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"唔止呢單<br />\n社評級條撚屌話唔推<br />\n但係官方文件仲見到會係香港推行"},{"pid":"2c2b82282dedc30517741e795bd4ef32e82557ef","tid":1309732,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2ed4f1f3b719d7a74674974f8b73c8bb331425","tid":1309732,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"連台灣報紙都咁報導"}]}